Guys, there's a simple way to get flitestar navdata updates. It was mentioned long ago but not too many people saw it.

Basically, download MagicISO, load your navdata cycle ( labelled 1108JVGB_2.iso) and change the filename in MagicISO from 1108JVGB_2.iso to 1108FSFM_2.iso, save it, remount the new file, and VOILA, flitemap navdata updates.
